The engineering society sponsors a resume review table near the stage, and career center staff log attendance metrics on laptops. An aroma of coffee and catered snacks spreads from the lounge. As the fair progresses, announcement chimes signal the final hour, during which students use tablets at kiosks to upload their resumes to the fair database. Additionally, a post-event survey link flashes on the monitors near the exit.

Concurrently, an alumni panel discusses how to prepare for technical interviews, and a startup founder invites students to a lunchtime pitch session. Some students rehearse elevator pitches quietly against the wall. As the event concludes, students exit with tote bags and a stack of business cards.
